{{version021}}
{{flavour|Spits a glob of acid at a nearby creature, covering it in corrosive slime for a short time. It may also splash onto other nearby creatures on impact.}}

'''Acid Splash''' launches a blob of [[acid]] at a targeted creature that deals damage and may inflict corrosion. It is similar to the [[Spit Acid]] ability present in [[oklob plant]]s and [[acid blob]]s and the like, but it may also splash onto creatures adjacent to the target.

{{monsters with spell}}
